index.html:
<html><head><script src="//npmci.syncfusion.com/development/demos/diagram/workflow-editor/datasource.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.syncfusion.com/ej2/24.1.41/dist/ej2.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.syncfusion.com/ej2/24.1.41/material.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
            body{
                touch-action:none;
            }
            .control-section{
                margin-top:100px;
            }
        </style></head><body><div class="stackblitz-container {{theme}}"><style>
    /* Toolbar Icon CSS */
    @font-face {
        font-family: "e-diagram-icons";
        src: url(data:application/x-font-ttf;charset=utf-8;base64,) format("truetype");
        font-weight: normal;
        font-style: normal;
    }

    .e-diagram-icons {
        font-family: "e-diagram-icons";
        speak: none;
        font-size: 54px;
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: normal;
        font-variant: normal;
        text-transform: none;
        line-height: 1;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    .e-diagram-reset::before {
        content: "\e715";
    }
    
    .e-reset::before {
        content: "\e715";
    }

    .e-play {
        content: '\e70C';
    }

    .loading-indicator {
        border: 4px solid #f3f3f3;
        border-top: 4px solid #3498db;
        border-radius: 50%;
        width: 15px;
        height: 15px;
        animation: spin 2s linear infinite;
    }


    .tick {
        display: none;
        animation: showTick 0.5s 0.2s forwards;
        font-size: 10px;
        width: 15px;
        height: 15px;
        padding-left: 4px;
        padding-top: 2.5px;
        line-height: 1;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .tick {
        background-color: green;
    }

    @keyframes spin {
        0% {
            transform: rotate(0deg);
        }

        100% {
            transform: rotate(360deg);
        }
    }

    @keyframes showTick {
        0% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.5);
        }

        100% {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1);
        }
    }
</style>

<div class="control-section">
    <div>
        <div style="width: 100%;height: 10%">
            <div id="toolbar" style="width:100%;margin-top: 10px;">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div id="diagram"></div>
            <div id="dialog"></div>
            <div id="endDialog"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


</div></body></html>
